title.narrative: Programme Costs for Economic Empowerment of the Poorest Programme

description.narrative: This activity (Programme Costs for Economic Empowerment of the Poorest Programme) is a component of Economic Empowerment of the Poorest reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Not for profit organisation' and a budget of £62,094,183. This component benefits Bangladesh, and works in the following sector(s): Social Protection, Environmental policy and administrative management, Urban development and management, Rural development. , with the following implementing partners: Harewelle International Limited. The start date is 01-11-2005 and the end date is 30-09-2016.
